{"tid":1904971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警：昨拘12男6女 15-51歲 曾有一名警員拔槍","createTime":"2020-03-01T02:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T04:00:40.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"29ec7561cb733d3bab985d36a9550968d9f1b6b9","tid":1904971,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T02:34:16.000Z","msg":"旺角示威衝突 警方拘捕18名男女<br />\n<br />\n港鐵太子站831事件發生六個月，大批人昨晚起在旺角一帶聚集，有人向警車擲汽油彈，又用雜物堵路及縱火，防暴警察到場，多度施放胡椒噴劑及發射催淚彈驅散，有警員一度舉起手槍。警方指，在現場共拘捕12男6女，年齡介乎15歲至51歲，涉嫌非法集結、盜竊、襲警及在公眾地方行為不檢等。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，一名男警在彌敦道與奶路臣街交界被多人以磚頭、石頭及竹枝等襲擊，在生命安全受嚴重威脅下，拔槍戒備，指涉事警員頭、手及腳受傷，連同另一名在豉油街及西洋菜南街交界被人襲擊的男警，送往明愛醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1270347&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1270347%26csid%3D261_341&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=c483de07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1270347&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"4de1a3d9b45eb7604bbef5537dfb2b7042e95a59","tid":1904971,"uid":32473,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"佢有受傷？<br />\n我好懷疑"},{"pid":"2dea952b6b3daf3b38a45625e9867ddf92f72652","tid":1904971,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4de1a3d9b45eb7604bbef5537dfb2b7042e95a59","tid":1904971,"uid":32473,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"佢有受傷？<br />\n我好懷疑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T02:37:20.000Z","msg":"蚊槍果時指甲撞到把槍掛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89aa999686a3000a85f698b0fabcf5158847965","tid":1904971,"uid":248131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T02:38:33.000Z","msg":"盜竊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戇尻要砌都搵條似樣啲嘅砌"},{"pid":"d576a0ce69c326b6a5f14c32db9